title: Preseason Studs in Week 2; Rookie QB Talk with Charley Casserly
itunes:title: Preseason Studs in Week 2; Rookie QB Talk with Charley Casserly
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling and Gregg Rosenthal bring you all of the latest news around the NFL including the Raiders demanding Antonio Brown "In or Out" (6:05) , Josh Gordon returning to the Patriots (12:17), and Josh McCown coming out of retirement (18:14). The heroes give their preseason week 2 takeaways (27:13) and then get to catch up with Charley Casserly to find out the meaning of the name " Joe Hardy" (44:02).
